snippet.title: Animal Hospital | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Young animal lovers are warmly invited to come and discover the fascinating world of Animal Hospital. Put on your vet gear, and get ready to save all the animals coming through the doors of your hospital. Soon you will learn everything there is to know about species from all four corners of the world!

Take care of adorable pets, wild and exotic animals, or even magical ones: cats, dogs, pandas, foxes, wolves, koalas, horses, unicorns… the more your clinic’s reputation is enhanced, the more visits from rare animals you will receive!

Out now on PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One and Nintendo Switch.
